"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-27-Medal-events-to-follow-at-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-on-July-27-1vzRHQBc4es-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  The competitions will continue at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics on Saturday night with more gold medals decided in the French capital. CGTN Sports Scene has the rundown for all of the finals taking place in the evening session on the first full day of competition at the Games.  The men's skateboarding\\u00a0street final will begin at 17:00 (GMT+2) at the Place de la Concord.  In swimming, the mens and women's 400-meter freestyle finals will take place at the Olympic Aquatics Centre in the Paris La Defense Arena at 20:42 (GMT+2), followed by the men's and women's 4\\u00c3\\u0097100-meter freestyle relay finals at 21:34 (GMT+2).  And the women's fencing epee individual gold medal bout will get underway at the Grand Palais at 21:30 (GMT+2).  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"